Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.68,0:00:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,树林那边的巴士站深处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.61,0:00:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对 就是登上坡道后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.53,0:00:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,位于前方的古老白色公馆里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.97,0:00:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说有一个长发的幽灵喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在着发之女王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.09,0:01:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像是杀人魔一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咔嚓 咔嚓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想剪断啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.26,0:01:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我的手把那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我要收拾掉所有胆敢扰乱这种关系的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能做到的话 那该有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.45,0:01:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 但是 做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.30,0:01:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.82,0:01:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是光想想就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.83,0:01:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头…头发 好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:02:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 刚才的是…对了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.62,0:02:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是灰村切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天 我偶然坐错了从学校回家的巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个长发的女幽灵喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是不小心回想起了那种传言而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:28.05,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是可疑分子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:30.65,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫灰村切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过传言倒是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿急救箱 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发拖到地上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我替你捧起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:02:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剪…剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请相信我 我是无意识中拿出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来 从来没有在人前拿出来过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这把剪刀 很早之前就一直在家里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候 我会用这把剪刀替人剪发
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家人们也非常开心的让我替他们剪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 大家逐渐开始去理发店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌我再去替他们剪发了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要剪头发的冲动 却依然很强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该说是直到现在兴趣也未曾改变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 所以才对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然做出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我觉得自己能够理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想给你剪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗 可以吗 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？真的真的？真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:33.95,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…剪不断的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从出生之后 头发一次都没有剪过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:04:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？咦？咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这把也不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么剪不断啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是被诅咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是武者小路祝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明名字是“祝福”来着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:05:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我也能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢这头长发喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小切…真是个奇怪的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算剪不断
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕光是抚摸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病院坂学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这个人刚才在温室那边受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以替他贴了创口贴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么多余的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了一般人别随便进来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活用品我就放这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐和我这就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…那个人并没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等 我拿外套
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.35,0:07:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么嘛 那两个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得太过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人是杀人魔！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准确的说 是杀人魔的后代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们持有祖传的杀人工具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们都是那个恐怖组织的成员 正监视着我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀人魔？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思 她不是看了什么漫画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不信啊 但是她说的一本正经的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子早就举目无亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.86,0:08:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正被某个团体保护着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 被害妄想症？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很早就失去了母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲也在几年前死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到她的头发了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子被诅咒了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟她走得太近 你也会没命的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 小切 你的额头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是摔了一跤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时至今日 当我看到女生的乌黑长发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是忍不住好想好想去剪掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定再也不花心了 有小祝在 要对她一心一意！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那头发…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剪不断
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发是女人的生命喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺滑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.16,0:10:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不合拍啊 灰村
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前一提到头发你就举止怪异起来多有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这说明我已经长大成人了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 高高在上的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 受欢迎的家伙就是不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么 我可是第一次听说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隔壁班的病院坂 来问了灰村的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那个 那个人给我感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是连人都要杀一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校生活好像很愉快嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不去学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我只上过小学低年级
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后 就因为这头发 被人嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:11:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我时不时 会做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦到我拥有普通的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在学校 和朋友聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新开张的糕点店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帅气的明星等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 终究是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终究只是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想剪掉它？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说“头发是女人的生命”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在一定范围内生长的话 或许是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我的头发 只是不断地变长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这是生命 我希望现在就杀了它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:12:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是已经给过你忠告了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这个人在一起 只会变得不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.30,0:13:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 让我很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙的父亲 已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是被你们杀了的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:31.35,english,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,660)}Killing Goods
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用杀害遗品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被杀？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:35.31,english,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(618,660)}Killing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀害…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这样啊 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来这家伙是代替你父亲的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺会见风使舵的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能做出那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛苦 自己一个人去忍受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的重负 不要让别人来担
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:02.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发之女王！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你灰村切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果都这么说了你还继续跟她来往
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们之间一定会决一死战的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 搞什么 这两个家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们持有祖传的杀人工具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:38.84,english,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(616,660)}Killing Goods
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀害遗品？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 小切 够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是死了比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这样的人 像我这样的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做什么 剪不断你头发的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎么了小切 你做什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.89,0:15:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 和爷爷没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是…因为你的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是从铁四郎那里听说的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近没跟爸爸打过电话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说啦到底是什么事 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的祖先出现过一个砍人的杀人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:15:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是说你的名字不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是担心你知道这件事会不会伤心才一直没说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会因为这点事就消沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 快告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H0F00E6&\bord0\be1\fs70\frz351.3\pos(436,226)}杀人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H0F00E6&\bord0\be1\fs70\frz351.3\pos(954,336)}诺马·格雷兰德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HF9761B&\bord0\be1\fs60\frz349.6\pos(480,636)}地下室的恶梦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.24,0:16:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有听说过这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该还有以此为原型拍成过电影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个著名的猎奇杀人事件的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把人搬到名为手术室的地下室里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将其剪裁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分尸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时他使用的凶器虽然众说纷纭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.19,0:17:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但普遍认为是一把小型的前端呈锯齿形的剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手持祖传的杀人工具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望现在就杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:13.87,english,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,660)}Killing Goods
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀害遗品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:19.23,english,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,660)}Killing Goods
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀害遗品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤独的活着 孤独的死去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这是正确的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 即使如此也有人愿意陪在我身边的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才正望着月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉有人要来杀我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我来杀你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是被小切杀死的话 或许也不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得白天说过的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.95,0:18:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的头发是剪不断的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是绝对不死的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀不死的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被诅咒了的…头发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这把剪刀说不定也被诅咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小祝有说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:18:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀人魔的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得有这可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且只有这把剪刀还没试过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我剪掉你的头发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:28.78,english,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,660)}长发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长发大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 如果是诅咒再称其为上帝就太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能剪断
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正准圆_GBK\fr270\fs80\c&H010101&\bord0\fsp30\pos(706,368)}拜托了··
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:19:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剪断了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 剪断了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的剪断了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如获新生的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小切是第一个杀死我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就叫它罪恶剪刀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪恶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.34,0:20:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是杀了至今为止的我的罪恶剪刀嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以是罪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:20:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫这名字行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正大家都受到了诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.63,0:21:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用起什么漂亮名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剪裁并分离的罪恶剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,断裁分离的罪恶剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好很好 罪恶剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖孩子乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后也请多关照啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是我在用它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请来剪断吧 我的小切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.89,0:23:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.96,0:23:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.22,0:23:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会这么处理的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.79,0:23:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.92,0:23:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.75,0:23:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,断裁分离的罪恶剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.11,0:23:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一话 异端的肖像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:39.98,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}窓を開けて見上げる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:46.51,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}あ　細い三日月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:52.63,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ガラス細工のように
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:59.23,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}煌くひかりで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:05.85,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}月よ　世界が消えるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:12.43,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}伝えて　いつか出会う一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:19.21,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ここで私は待ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:25.06,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}闇にほしかえて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:31.87,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ずっと　My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:35.84,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}願いを届け　星も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.11,0:21:39.15,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}何が起ころうと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:45.27,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}君に会える時まで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:49.03,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}透き通った孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:52.42,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}胸に抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:58.11,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}君を呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.78,0:22:10.05,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}心から応援
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.26,0:22:25.13,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}浅い眠りの中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:31.69,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}不思議な夢見た
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:38.17,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}君に守られていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.86,0:22:44.48,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}月影の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.71,0:22:51.13,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}どんな運命 巡っても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:57.55,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}必ず君と出会うために
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:22:59.57,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}強く…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:39.98,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}推开窗户仰望天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:46.51,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}啊 挂着细长的新月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:52.63,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}如玻璃工艺品般
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:59.23,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:05.85,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}明月啊 如果世界要消亡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:12.43,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}请转达某一刻将出现的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:19.21,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我在这里等着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:25.06,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}即使星空再变换
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:31.87,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}永远都是 My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:35.84,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}请传达我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.11,0:21:39.15,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}连星星也按耐不住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:45.27,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}直到与你相见之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:49.03,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}将清澈透明的孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:52.42,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}紧紧抱在胸前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:58.11,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}呼唤着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.78,0:22:10.05,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}打心底为你加油
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.26,0:22:25.13,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}浅睡之中的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:31.69,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}一场不可思议的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:38.17,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}在被你守护着的
